<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>【new】XHunt 数据统计</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        .header p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .auth-info {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logout-btn {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            color: white;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .logout-btn:hover {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        /* 快捷链接样式 */
        .quick-links {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .quick-links h3 {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .links-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .link-item {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
        }

        .link-item:hover {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .link-item a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .link-item a:hover {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .link-icon {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            min-width: 30px;
        }

        .link-text {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .link-title {
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 3px;
        }

        .link-desc {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        /* 统计数据样式 */
        .stats-section {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .stat-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .stat-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .stat-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .stat-title {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .stat-value {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .section {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .tags-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .tag-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
        }

        .tag-name {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #374151;
        }

        .tag-count {
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            padding: 4px 8px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .distribution-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .distribution-item {
            padding: 16px;
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .user-info {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .user-name {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #667eea;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .user-username {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }

        .user-stats {
            text-align: right;
        }

        .review-count {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #374151;
        }

        .user-rank {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        .kol-badge {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #f59e0b, #d97706);
            color: white;
            padding: 2px 8px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-left: 8px;
        }

        .refresh-info {
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            margin-top: 20px;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .stats-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .header h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .stat-value {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .auth-info {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 10px;
            }

            .links-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .distribution-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="auth-info">
            <span>🔐 已认证访问 - 统计数据面板 [server-byteplus]</span>
            <a href="/api/xhunt/stats/logout" class="logout-btn">退出登录</a>
        </div>

        <!-- 快捷链接区域 -->
        <div class="quick-links">
            <h3>🚀 快捷入口</h3>
            <div class="links-grid">
                <div class="link-item">
                    <a href="https://analytics.google.com/analytics/web/#/p484087839/reports/intelligenthome" target="_blank">
                        <span class="link-icon">📊</span>
                        <div class="link-text">
                            <div class="link-title">Google Analytics</div>
                            <div class="link-desc">网站流量统计分析</div>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>

                <div class="link-item">
                    <a href="https://us5.datadoghq.com/apm/home" target="_blank">
                        <span class="link-icon">🐕</span>
                        <div class="link-text">
                            <div class="link-title">DataDog APM</div>
                            <div class="link-desc">应用性能监控</div>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>

                <div class="link-item">
                    <a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/devconsole/9d25eceb-fe8d-401a-a54e-08499569b9a3" target="_blank">
                        <span class="link-icon">🧩</span>
                        <div class="link-text">
                            <div class="link-title">Chrome 开发者控制台</div>
                            <div class="link-desc">浏览器插件管理</div>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>

                <div class="link-item">
                    <a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1W4URRutiCIxtYy8oLgEp8wy9yAzRDbNpIbNeXB2oors/edit?tab=t.0" target="_blank">
                        <span class="link-icon">📝</span>
                        <div class="link-text">
                            <div class="link-title">需求文档</div>
                            <div class="link-desc">产品需求与规划</div>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>

                <div class="link-item">
                    <a href="https://kb.cryptohunt.ai/nacos/" target="_blank">
                        <span class="link-icon">⚙️</span>
                        <div class="link-text">
                            <div class="link-title">Nacos 配置中心</div>
                            <div class="link-desc">服务配置管理</div>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="header">
            <h1>📊 XHunt 数据统计</h1>
            <p>实时产品数据监控面板 - <%= formatDateTime() %></p>
        </div>

        <!-- 统计数据区域 -->
        <div class="stats-section">
            <!-- 核心指标（移除昨日对比） -->
            <div class="stats-grid">
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-header">
                        <span class="stat-title">📱 日活用户(已登录X)</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-value"><%= formatNumber(stats.coreMetrics.dailyActiveUsers.value) %></div>
                </div>

                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-header">
                        <span class="stat-title">💬 今日评论</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-value"><%= formatNumber(stats.coreMetrics.dailyReviews.value) %></div>
                </div>

                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-header">
                        <span class="stat-title">👥 评论用户</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-value"><%= formatNumber(stats.coreMetrics.dailyReviewUsers.value) %></div>
                </div>

                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-header">
                        <span class="stat-title">🆕 新注册用户(已登录X)</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-value"><%= formatNumber(stats.coreMetrics.dailyNewUsers.value) %></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 累计数据 -->
            <div class="section">
                <h2 class="section-title">📈 累计数据</h2>
                <div class="stats-grid">
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-title">总用户数</div>
                        <div class="stat-value"><%= formatNumber(stats.totalMetrics.totalUsers) %></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-title">总账号数</div>
                        <div class="stat-value"><%= formatNumber(stats.totalMetrics.totalAccounts) %></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-title">KOL 用户数</div>
                        <div class="stat-value"><%= formatNumber(stats.totalMetrics.totalKOLUsers) %></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-title">累计积分</div>
                        <div class="stat-value"><%= formatNumber(stats.totalMetrics.totalPointsAwarded) %></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-title">平均评分</div>
                        <div class="stat-value"><%= stats.totalMetrics.averageRating %> ⭐</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-title">今日积分</div>
                        <div class="stat-value"><%= formatNumber(stats.todayDetails.pointsAwarded) %></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 周期统计 -->
            <div class="section">
                <h2 class="section-title">📅 周期统计</h2>
                <div class="stats-grid">
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-title">本周评论</div>
                        <div class="stat-value"><%= formatNumber(stats.periodMetrics.weekly.reviews) %></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-title">本周新用户</div>
                        <div class="stat-value"><%= formatNumber(stats.periodMetrics.weekly.newUsers) %></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-title">本月评论</div>
                        <div class="stat-value"><%= formatNumber(stats.periodMetrics.monthly.reviews) %></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-title">本月新用户</div>
                        <div class="stat-value"><%= formatNumber(stats.periodMetrics.monthly.newUsers) %></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 热门标签 -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">🏷️ 热门标签 TOP 10</h2>
            <div class="tags-grid">
                <% stats.popularTags.forEach(tag => { %>
                    <div class="tag-item">
                        <span class="tag-name"><%= tag.name %></span>
                        <span class="tag-count"><%= tag.count %></span>
                    </div>
                <% }); %>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 用户活跃度分布（显示用户名） -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">👑 活跃用户排行榜 TOP 20</h2>
            <div class="distribution-grid">
                <% stats.userDistribution.forEach((user, index) => { %>
                    <div class="distribution-item">
                        <div class="user-info">
                            <div>
                                <div class="user-name">
                                    #<%= index + 1 %> <%= user.displayName || user.username || '匿名用户' %>
                                    <% if (user.kolRank) { %>
                                        <span class="kol-badge">KOL</span>
                                    <% } %>
                                </div>
                                <% if (user.username) { %>
                                    <div class="user-username">@<%= user.username %></div>
                                <% } %>
                            </div>
                            <div class="user-stats">
                                <div class="review-count"><%= user.reviewCount %> 条评论</div>
                                <% if (user.kolRank) { %>
                                    <div class="user-rank">KOL排名: <%= formatNumber(user.kolRank) %></div>
                                <% } %>
                                <% if (user.classification) { %>
                                    <div class="user-rank">分类: <%= user.classification %></div>
                                <% } %>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% }); %>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 🔥有灵魂的KOL 标签专业统计 -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">🔥 "有灵魂的KOL" 标签专业统计</h2>
            
            <!-- 统计概览 -->
            <div class="stats-grid" style="margin-bottom: 30px;">
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-title">今日使用次数</div>
                    <div class="stat-value"><%= formatNumber(stats.kolTagAnalytics.stats.todayUsage) %></div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-title">累计使用次数</div>
                    <div class="stat-value"><%= formatNumber(stats.kolTagAnalytics.stats.totalUsage) %></div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-title">参与评论用户数</div>
                    <div class="stat-value"><%= formatNumber(stats.kolTagAnalytics.stats.uniqueUsers) %></div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-title">被评论账号数</div>
                    <div class="stat-value"><%= formatNumber(stats.kolTagAnalytics.stats.uniqueAccounts) %></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 评论者排行榜 -->
            <div style="margin-bottom: 30px;">
                <h3 style="font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #374151; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; padding-left: 12px;">
                    🏆 评论者排行榜 TOP 20 - 谁最爱打这个标签
                </h3>
                <div class="distribution-grid">
                    <% if (stats.kolTagAnalytics.reviewers && stats.kolTagAnalytics.reviewers.length > 0) { %>
                        <% stats.kolTagAnalytics.reviewers.forEach((reviewer, index) => { %>
                            <div class="distribution-item" style="border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;">
                                <div class="user-info">
                                    <div>
                                        <div class="user-name">
                                            #<%= index + 1 %> <%= reviewer.displayName || reviewer.username || '匿名用户' %>
                                            <% if (reviewer.isKOL) { %>
                                                <span class="kol-badge">KOL</span>
                                            <% } %>
                                        </div>
                                        <% if (reviewer.username) { %>
                                            <div class="user-username">@<%= reviewer.username %></div>
                                        <% } %>
                                        <% if (reviewer.classification) { %>
                                            <div class="user-rank">分类: <%= reviewer.classification %></div>
                                        <% } %>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="user-stats">
                                        <div class="review-count" style="color: #f59e0b;">
                                            <%= reviewer.tagUsageCount %> 次使用
                                        </div>
                                        <% if (reviewer.kolRank20W) { %>
                                            <div class="user-rank">KOL排名: <%= formatNumber(reviewer.kolRank20W) %></div>
                                        <% } %>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        <% }); %>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <div style="text-align: center; color: #6b7280; padding: 40px;">
                            暂无数据
                        </div>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 被评论者排行榜 -->
            <div>
                <h3 style="font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #374151; border-left: 4px solid #10b981; padding-left: 12px;">
                    🎯 被评论者排行榜 TOP 20 - 谁最受认可
                </h3>
                <div class="distribution-grid">
                    <% if (stats.kolTagAnalytics.receivers && stats.kolTagAnalytics.receivers.length > 0) { %>
                        <% stats.kolTagAnalytics.receivers.forEach((receiver, index) => { %>
                            <div class="distribution-item" style="border-left: 4px solid #10b981;">
                                <div class="user-info">
                                    <div>
                                        <div class="user-name">
                                            #<%= index + 1 %> <%= receiver.displayName || receiver.handle || '未知账号' %>
                                        </div>
                                        <% if (receiver.handle) { %>
                                            <div class="user-username">@<%= receiver.handle %></div>
                                        <% } %>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="user-stats">
                                        <div class="review-count" style="color: #10b981;">
                                            <%= receiver.receivedTagCount %> 次被评
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        <% }); %>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <div style="text-align: center; color: #6b7280; padding: 40px;">
                            暂无数据
                        </div>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="refresh-info">
            <p>🔄 数据每次访问时实时更新 | ⏰ 最后更新: <%= formatDateTime() %></p>
            <p style="margin-top: 8px; font-size: 14px;">🕐 所有统计数据均按中国时区（UTC+8）计算</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // 自动刷新页面（每5分钟）
        setTimeout(() => {
            window.location.reload();
        }, 5 * 60 * 1000);
    </script>
</body>
</html>